      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This vehicle is in honest, poor condition and definitely shows its age with significant cosmetic and mechanical wear, but it still has potential for the right owner! It\u2019s an ideal choice for someone handy with tools or looking for a very affordable entry-point vehicle. Come take a look and see if this is the fixer-upper you've been searching for!",
