    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. It is mechanically sound, providing a smooth and reliable driving experience. While the exterior and interior are generally clean and well-preserved, you may find some minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with regular use, such as small stone chips on the hood and light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Overall, it is a solid, dependable car that is ready for the road.",
