    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserved in absolute pristine condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish without a single swirl mark, stone chip, or blemish. Inside, the cabin remains untouched by time; the premium leather upholstery retains its original scent and firm bolsters, while the carpets and trim are entirely spotless. Every electronic component and mechanical system functions flawlessly, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history from day one. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
